    Simple parser which knows how to parse BytesSegment representations of persisted HighPerformanceLogEvents.

    The format of events on disk is:

    • Total event length: 4 bytes (excludes the length field itself)
    • File position: 8 bytes (the starting position in the original log file)
    • Serialized HighPerformanceLogEvent: variable length
